title: SPY Hits Bear Mtn. for the 8th Annual Hot Dawgs and Handrails
description: Over this glorious weekend, while most of you where on the beach bronzing, getting pitted or sleeping off your hang over, SPY spent our saturday up at Bear Mtn. for the 8th annual Hotdawgs and Handrails kicking off fall and getting the masses hyped on the up-coming winter. Spectators from all over southern California came and enjoyed discount prices on season passes, a tent city filled with games and prizes and a handrail contest on snow trucked in, chopped up, and spread out. Needless to say, wicked boarding went down.
